# VHS documentation
# https://github.com/charmbracelet/vhs#installation

Output how_to_use_jan.mp4

Require opencode

Set Shell "zsh"
Set FontSize 28
Set Width 1600
Set Height 900
Set TypingSpeed 140ms

Type "mkdir -p ~/student-agent-pack-demo && cd ~/student-agent-pack-demo"
Enter
Sleep 3s

Hide
Type "opencode"
Enter
Sleep 6s
Show

Type "I want to work on E3."
Enter
Sleep 8s
